simplenlg.realiser
Class AnchorString

java.lang.Object
  simplenlg.realiser.AnchorString

public class AnchorString
extends Object

AnchorString contains a String and an Anchor. It is a construct necessary for WYSIWYM feedback texts. This version of simpleNLG has been adapted to return lists of AnchorStrings, instead of concatenated Strings.

Version:
1.0 24-11-2006
Author:
Feikje Hielkema
